docs.text: Welcome to MkDocs # For full documentation visit mkdocs.org . Commands # mkdocs new [dir-name] - Create a new project. mkdocs serve - Start the live-reloading docs server. mkdocs build - Build the documentation site. mkdocs -h - Print help message and exit. mkdocs gh-deploy - build & push your project docs into gh-pages branch and deploy it to GitHub Pages . Project layout # mkdocs.yml # The configuration file. docs/ index.md # The documentation homepage. ... # Other markdown pages, images and other files.

The application will copy the KYC files of Perseus/Flexcube accounts from a temporary directory into a permanent directory. Copy KYC Files Flowchart #
docs.title: Copy KYC

docs.text: It is a Java desktop application. We normally set a scheduled job on server to trigger the application to run every midnight. The application will copy the KYC files of Perseus/Flexcube accounts from a temporary directory into a permanent directory.
